 *  2 |   3.14E+00 |       3.00E+08 |      7.26E-03 |
 *  3 |  3.142E+00 |      2.998E+08 |     7.257E-03 |
 *  4 | 3.1416E+00 |     2.9979E+08 |    7.2574E-03 |
 *
 *  General format (%G) :
 *
 *  d |     pi     | speed of light | fine structure
 *  ---+------------+----------------+----------------
 *  1 |          3 |          3E+08 |         0.007 |
 *  2 |        3.1 |        3.0E+08 |        0.0073 |
 *  3 |       3.14 |       3.00E+08 |       0.00726 |
 *  4 |      3.142 |      2.998E+08 |      0.007257 |
*/

